[normal]Introduction[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Local Roads[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Road Salt[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](a) retaining a national strategic salt reserve of 425,000 tonnes and 
[normal]ensuring that we have robust distribution procedures in place
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](b) publishing an updated note on the Department for Transport website (at end of each October) which provides local highway authorities with details on how to access the strategic salt stockpi
[normal]le if it is required; and 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal](c) continuing to monitor salt stocks of highway authorities across 
[normal]England
[normal], 
[normal]Scotland
[normal] and 
[normal]Wales
[normal] hold.
